room_title: Escape room "Sweet Revenge" by Quandary Escape Rooms in Sacramento
room_description: Welcome to the Candy Shop. Ronald Cates has hired your team to infiltrate Anderson's Confectionary to steal back Grandma's Secret Recipe. Anderson's is protected by the SASSI Security Company, but  Luckily R.Cates has already scouted ahead to ensure that you'll get past the system. Additionally an escape route has been paved, as leaving through the front door with Grandma's Recipe is a sure way to get caught. What secret is Anderson hiding, and will you make it out before the SASSI System comes back online??
